DOC.brief_summary: A multiple-dose , double-blind , randomize , four-week , three-treatment , parallel study 66 healthy adult subject receive 6 capsules/d , administer dose 1.3 g/d eicosapentaenoic acid ( EPA ) +docosahexaenoic acid ( DHA ) fish oil ethyl ester ( EE ) , fish oil triglyceride ( TG ) krill oil total 4 week . The objective study compare oral bioavailability EPA+DHA total plasma across three formulation end 4 week study .
DOC.brief_title: A Parallel Bioavailability Study Fish Oil-Ethyl Ester Versus Fish Oil-Triglyceride Versus Krill Oil
